{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41079, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "66989363": {"uid": 66989363, "username": "UID:66989363", "credit": 135275008, "medal": null, "reputation": "147_-300", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1762774156, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 2701, "rvrc": 10, "money": 0, "thisvisit": 1782082361, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135275008}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "66989363": -300, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"pid": 857612260, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 21:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "当然 最基础那些 多头趋势 空头趋势 破位 企稳 突破 等等这些还是要记的。", "lou": 760, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770644598}, {"pid": 857614487, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 22:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857613453,45974302,1370]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-02-09 21:58):[/b]<br/><br/>很难学，狼大，真的很难[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>这比考公难?你要和一亿人同场竞技 而且还有大资金 你啥都不学还想赢 是不是痴人说梦了", "lou": 761, "content_length": 82, "reply_to": 857613453, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770646232}, {"pid": 857615230, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 22:18", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "[E1770646910 0 0]\t", "content": "[quote][pid=857613651,45974302,1370]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67087103]-咬我[/uid] (2026-02-09 22:01):[/b]<br/><br/>个人见解，学了那么多之后我觉得缠论比其他的讲的都清楚很多(没有踩一捧一)，只不过学习难度也很高[s:ac:愁][/quote]<br/>音符那里有个用缠论的还行的 虽然废话很多 我看了两次大概知道是什么水平  名字是  都XX [color=red]不是引流 只是个人看到[/color]<br/>噢 编辑了", "lou": 762, "content_length": 105, "reply_to": 857613651, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770646681}, {"pid": 857617117, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 85, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 22:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "为啥说这个呢 因为根据大家平均年龄25-45这个年龄段 基本上不可能看书了，能系统沉下心跟书且弄懂意思的可能性在我看来非常低。<br/>所以还是需要一些基础启蒙的。我这么说希望大家不要介意，毕竟我自认只是刚入门<br/><br/>这个市场如果不是这两年至少还是牛市行情 指数超过3000 平均股价也一直再涨，很多人是挣不到钱的。也就是赚钱基数大了，所以覆盖到了你们而已。", "lou": 763, "content_length": 323, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770647947}, {"pid": 857617888, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 22:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857617589,45974302,1371]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64571355]水无艮[/uid] (2026-02-09 22:44):[/b]<br/><br/>我只能说ai时代帮助学习很多 以前一些看似是经验学说的东西都能被ai解释并且探求其中的底层逻辑 各位狼崽一定要多用起来呀[s:ac:上][/quote]<br/>AI解释不是不能用 但是最好是自己先理解 再看视频讲解 最后用至少2个以上AI工具解释，这样对照起来才能知道是否理解对了<br/>特别是刚用AI，没有长期训练的就偶尔问一下的那种AI解释还是蛮多错的，这种定义的上的错误不是影响挣钱 而是加速亏钱", "lou": 764, "content_length": 222, "reply_to": 857617589, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770648461}, {"pid": 857618782, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-09 22:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857618617,45974302,1371]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61851201]huining222[/uid] (2026-02-09 22:55):[/b]<br/><br/>我感觉用AI，我得学会如何提问[/quote]<br/>对的， 只有懂得越多，不懂的才越多", "lou": 765, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 857618617, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770649035}, {"pid": 857786207, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 118, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 10:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "趁中继旭创那些破位杀  可以去找被带下来的AI硬了 很多AI硬分支都调整到位了 <br/>还有 不要听那些小作坊说 今天卖票  明天买逆回购 后天再买票去套利的<br/>可能不仅丢了芝麻 西瓜也看不到。<br/>只要节前不大涨 大概率持股过节", "lou": 766, "content_length": 186, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770776435}, {"pid": 857786987, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 10:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857786849,45974302,1414]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=786758]Aracher[/uid] (2026-02-11 10:24):[/b]<br/><br/>北部湾这个板是鱼大砸的吧[s:ac:闪光][/quote]<br/>我没有 2000万一毛钱都不卖  我说了我等通航", "lou": 767, "content_length": 43, "reply_to": 857786849, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770776749}, {"pid": 857787987, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 81, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 10:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这几天处理国外资产回国  不太得空看帖，能做完操作就不错了<br/>虽然期货挣很多 但是手续费  汇率 操作团队的奖金一给完也是去了好大一块肉。。特别是汇率。。。升值对我就没那么友好了", "lou": 768, "content_length": 162, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770777135}, {"pid": 857789554, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 10:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202602/11/jmQ1aw-37mlK8T1kSeb-1c.jpg[/img]<br/>因为我真带他挣钱了[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 769, "content_length": 54, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202602/11/jmQ1aw-37mlK8T1kSeb-1c.jpg", "size": 9, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202602/11", "name": "jmQ1aw-37mlK8T1kSeb-1c.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770777747}, {"pid": 857812151, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 69, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 13:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "指数绝对值才10个点的幅度。。。。。。。。。。。。。缩量到2WE以下了<br/>这里怕什么 怕大跌？没有的事", "lou": 770, "content_length": 91, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770788193}, {"pid": 857812934, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 80, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 13:43", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "提前说一下 只要明后天没有指数级别大涨<br/>我活跃仓位80%仓位以上过节<br/>10%资源 35%半导体类(包含光刻机光刻胶) 20%AI硬 10%机器人 5%打野<br/>因为我调了钱回来  目前总仓位比之前大了不少。<br/>长线仓不动", "lou": 771, "content_length": 171, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770788585}, {"pid": 857813556, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 13:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857813266,45974302,1429]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60220546]知者默[/uid] (2026-02-11 13:45):[/b]<br/><br/>非银金融不配置吗狼大[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>不配 我剩指南针的底仓  过4117已经做到了  我已经达成了我的任务<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202602/11/jmQ1aw-lcfhKcT1kShg-1i.jpg[/img]", "lou": 772, "content_length": 99, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202602/11/jmQ1aw-lcfhKcT1kShg-1i.jpg", "size": 13, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202602/11", "name": "jmQ1aw-lcfhKcT1kShg-1i.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "56"}], "reply_to": 857813266, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770788890}, {"pid": 857813784, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 10, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 13:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857813532,45974302,1429]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1890271]坚强的小p孩[/uid] (2026-02-11 13:48):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 不拿航天了么[/quote]<br/>不拿了  昨天换了石油", "lou": 773, "content_length": 23, "reply_to": 857813532, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770789010}, {"pid": 857869983, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 22:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我的长线账户和你们的固收一样 只有调仓换股止盈止损，包括之前的比亚迪 安克创新止盈，然后现在的铝 稀土 摩托车等还在持有 长线重点是不用看分时，只用看消息和月K", "lou": 774, "content_length": 149, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1770819192}, {"pid": 857870740, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-11 22:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我目前活跃仓位能力上限就是6个 多了看不过来<br/>赚的钱就往长线账户里面放，长线这部分正常都是翻倍起步，只是时间不一定 反正票没暴雷肯定是翻倍以上的<br/>然后还有海外期货，所以精力只能操作这么多了<br/>有时候关注期货的时候股票就不能看了，所以只能找了个交易员来按策略操作", "lou": 775, "content_length": 247, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1770819637}, {"pid": 857906695, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 68, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 09:38", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们怕什么？怕挣钱？", "lou": 776, "content_length": 20, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770860321}, {"pid": 857908686, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 92, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 09:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我敢这里说能有机会加仓的 你们要珍惜<br/>当然 我明确说明 易中天26年幅度  不如  上游和周边任何一个。天是蹭上了光而已 那就排除天", "lou": 777, "content_length": 112, "14": {"13": 2}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770861208}, {"pid": 857911100, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 39, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 10:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=857910477,45974302,1458]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=10253715]stephaniel[/uid] (2026-02-12 10:06):[/b]<br/><br/>半导体设备究竟是怎么做到每日亏钱的，我不理解[/quote]<br/>一周跌不到1个点  亏在哪？", "lou": 778, "content_length": 28, "reply_to": 857910477, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770862229}, {"pid": 857911528, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-02-12 10:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "易中绿了  我不是唱衰 我只是说事实<br/>我的预判成功率你们应该是了解的。", "lou": 779, "content_length": 62, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1770862417}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155486, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109223, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "江东jump", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109230, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,62799978,60424140,42468630,61560061,67096060,61021164,67102441,63220970,19312329,60694817,67086969,67061200,60701305,66937546,62357329,41746951,60027718,,39248719,62403348,40776497,67088120,66875016,64268963,1459804,67062343,12177085,38702942,1383368,67093370,66885146,40024017,63922791,67095295,66895557,64571355,62824316,5495109,38806682,67122547,67137453,67078475,,38110681,66618696,64658121,67085304,38883076,67132556,67126715,62653482,67128658,64731349,67105